OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens have pledged to
OL,7,Finvest #600 million in renewables in a
OL,8,Fmove they said would cut bills and
OL,9,Fprotect the planet.
OL,11,FThe party said the investment in wind,
OL,12,Fwave and solar would be in part funded
OL,13,Fby scrapping millions in public
OL,14,Ffunding for "unproven" carbon capture
OL,15,Fand storage technology.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@VO]
