OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FCo-leaders Gillian Mackay and Ross
OL,7,FGreer announced the manifesto
OL,8,Fcommitment ahead of a visit to South
OL,9,FLanarkshire College where they will
OL,10,Fmeet with students training in green
OL,11,Fenergy skills.
OL,13,FIn a bid to combat rising energy
OL,14,Fprices due to the war in Iran, the
OL,15,FGreens called for the UK Government to
OL,16,Fde-link cheaper electricity prices
OL,17,Ffrom "extortionate" international gas
OL,18,Fprices.
OL,26,@yD@FOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FMs Mackay said: "Scotland has a huge
OL,7,Frenewables potential but we are not
OL,8,Fyet meeting it.
OL,10,F"Green energy is the cleanest and
OL,11,Fcheapest energy available, but the
OL,12,Fother parties are caught in a loop of
OL,13,Farguing for more fossil fuels.
OL,15,F"With the right support we can lower
OL,16,Fbills, cut carbon emissions and create
OL,17,Fthousands of good, well-paid jobs that
OL,18,Fwill last for years to come and put us
OL,19,Fat the forefront of a vital and
OL,20,Fgrowing industry."
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@AOUwD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FMs Mackay said the planet could not
OL,7,Fafford the burning of any more fossil
OL,8,Ffuels and called for a green
OL,9,Ftransition that supported oil and gas
OL,10,Fworkers.
OL,12,FBut she said that transition could not
OL,13,Fhappen without the Scottish and UK
OL,14,Fgovernments, adding: "We have seen
OL,15,Fwhat happened at Grangemouth and
OL,16,FMossmorran when the jobs left but our
OL,17,FGovernments failed to plan for it and
OL,18,Fthe communities were made to pay the
OL,19,Fprice.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,F"It's time for us to seize the huge
OL,7,Fopportunity we have on our doorsteps
OL,8,Fand support the green jobs of the
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,F"Scotland has the talent, resources
OL,12,Fand ambition to lead, now all we need
OL,13,Fis a government who will give it their
OL,14,Ffull backing.
OL,16,F"Keeping people locked into gas is
OL,17,Fwrecking our planet and punishing
OL,18,Fhouseholds with outrageous costs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,F"Meanwhile, fossil fuel giants are
OL,7,Fraking in massive profits and laughing
OL,8,Ftheir way to the bank.
OL,10,F"By rapidly expanding clean energy and
OL,11,Freducing our reliance on oil and gas
OL,12,Fwe can start to bring down bills and
OL,13,Fput money back in people's pockets.
OL,15,F"A vote for the Scottish Greens on May
OL,16,F7 is a vote to cut bills, tackle fuel
OL,17,Fpoverty and finally end our dependence
OL,18,Fon volatile fossil fuels."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
