OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FScottish Tory energy spokesman Douglas
OL,7,FLumsden described the Greens as
OL,8,F"extremists", who "egged on Labour and
OL,9,Fthe SNP in their destruction of our
OL,10,Foil and gas industry".
OL,12,F"Renewables alone are not enough to
OL,13,Fmeet our energy needs," he said.
OL,15,F"It's just common sense that to lower
OL,16,Fenergy bills we need to drill the
OL,17,FNorth Sea, invest in nuclear and
OL,18,Fexpand renewables but we're the only
OL,19,Fparty saying this.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]pD@SOUrD@UO]tD@AOUuD@WO]wD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,F"The Greens' plans would result in
OL,7,Fmonster pylons and huge battery
OL,8,Fsubstations scarring our countryside
OL,9,Fand local communities wouldn't get a
OL,10,Flook in."
OL,12,FScottish Labour finance spokesman
OL,13,FMichael Marra said it was "laughable"
OL,14,Ffor the Greens to push for a just
OL,15,Ftransition while being against nuclear
OL,16,Fenergy.
OL,18,F"The only way we achieve lower bills
OL,19,Fand energy security is by using all of
OL,20,Fthe resources, skills and
OL,21,Fopportunities Scotland has," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]uD@[OUuD@eO]zD@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,F"Scottish Labour has already announced
OL,7,Fplans to make heating your home
OL,8,Fcheaper through widening eligibility
OL,9,Ffor the Warmer Homes Scotland grant
OL,10,Fcreating a warmer homes programme,
OL,11,Fboosting the uptake of the Warm Home
OL,12,FDiscount and topping up grants for
OL,13,Frural homeowners.
OL,15,F"We will also end the SNP and Greens'
OL,16,Fideological block on new nuclear
OL,17,Fenergy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
