FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774929839
OL,3,CGreens pledge #600m renewables
OL,4,Cinvestment through carbon capture cuts
OL,6,FSNP candidate for Aberdeen Donside,
OL,7,FJackie Dunbar, said: "The SNP put in
OL,8,Fplace a #500 million Just Transition
OL,9,FFund to support renewables expansion,
OL,10,Fbut the single biggest barrier to
OL,11,Frenewables development in Scotland is
OL,12,FLabour's tax on Scotland's energy and
OL,13,Fcrippling transmission charges from
OL,14,FWestminster.
OL,16,F"Only a vote for the SNP can deliver a
OL,17,Ffresh start with independence ` giving
OL,18,Fus the powers to end Westminster's
OL,19,Fwaste of our energy potential and the
OL,20,Fpower to lower energy bills for
OL,21,FScottish households and businesses."
OL,26,@oD@VOUxD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
